nodes.documentation:
he Oracle contract provides the reference prices for the contracts.  Currently the Oracle is 
pdated by an off chain calculation by DDA.  Methodology can be found at 
ww.github.com/DecentralizedDerivatives/Oracles
nodes.name: Oracle

dev Constructor, sets two public api strings
.g. "json(https://api.gdax.com/products/BTC-USD/ticker).price"
"json(https://api.binance.com/api/v3/ticker/price?symbol=BTCUSDT).price"
or "json(https://api.gdax.com/products/ETH-USD/ticker).price"
"json(https://api.binance.com/api/v3/ticker/price?symbol=ETHUSDT).price"
